    <title>b9586: webui: implement pinned conversations support (#21387)</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;webui: implement pinned conversations support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;webui: linter/prettier pass&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
